DESCRIPTION:Link: https://hulms.instructure.com/courses/4981/discussion_topics/61912\n\nHello everyone\nI'll be your TA for CS 435- GenAI this semester. I hope you guys have a great time in the course.I'll be keeping my Ehsas Hours on Wednesdays 10:00-11:00hrs in the Projects Lab. Feel free to reach me out this time for course-related questions or guidance.\nApart from that\, feel free to drop me a message on teams if you need any help.\nRegards\,Muhammad Anas (ma08458)
