BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260201
DESCRIPTION:Link: https://hulms.instructure.com/courses/5111/discussion_topics/62168\n\nHi all\,\nI’ve uploaded the first programming assignment. This assignment wraps up the mathematical foundations of Large Language Models (LLMs). This assignment will be due February 15th at 11:59 PM (two weeks from now).\nThe assignments will be guided and relatively straightforward. That said\, I strongly recommend starting early. Fully understanding what’s being asked will take some time. Completing the assignments carefully will also prepare you well for the quizzes and the midterm.\nStarting this week\, we’ll focus exclusively on neural models for language modeling. From there\, we’ll gradually build toward sequence-to-sequence translation\, which will motivate our transition to Attention-based models.\nBest\,Usama
