DESCRIPTION:Link: https://hulms.instructure.com/courses/5040/discussion_topics/61937\n\nDear Kaavish Students\,\nCareer City 2026 is being held on 29th January from 10-5 pm and will be featuring 100+ organization\, mentorship on a first come first served basis with senior leaders in the industry\, a chance to get your LinkedIn photo taken and engage more deeply through the industry showcasing area where organizations will be showing their product demos and offerings. Come prepared with your resume and elevator pitch and in case you need help\, you can come to the career city orientation tomorrow at 1pm in Tariq Rafi.Pls download hive to ensure your attendance is marked as this event is mandatory for juniors and seniors.\nSee you all!\nOffice of Career Services
